Hello there,

If you're looking for an Ex Neuroscientist, who really loves solving problems, both in the physical world and with code, you've come to the right place.

I'll be adding projects at @ishtargate as I go along. Hopefully they will soon include a mobile app, desktop app, and some web stuff.

I'll be listing some projects here:

But for now it's just https://gihub.com/ishtargate.
